Board chairmen and members have received their appointment letters four months after they were inaugurated by the FCT minister, Muhammad Musa Bello. Chairman of the All Progressives Congress (APC) in the FCT, Alhaji Usman Abdulmalik, presented the appointment letters to them last Thursday at the state secretariat of the party in Abuja. The APC chairman, while congratulating the board chairmen and their members, charged them to live above board in discharging their duties. Among the board chairmen that received their letters are, Alhaji Musa Yahaya Muhammad, Board Chairman for FCT SEB, Alhaji Abubakar Jibrin Giri, Board Chairman, FCT ScholarshipÂ  and Isah Ramat Kwali, Board Chairman; FCT Area Councils Services Commission.